-- BP Says It Has Stopped Flow of Oil to Gulf
-- Katarzyna Klimasinska
-- 2010-07-15T20:05:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/bp-says-oil-stopped-flowing-into-gulf-as-pressure-tests-conducted-on-well.html

          
          
             BP Plc said oil has stopped flowing
into the Gulf of Mexico for the first time in about three months
as the company pressure tests its damaged Macondo well. Senior
Vice President Kent Wells commented today on a conference call.  
          
          


  


        